    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 1 157 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}Happy New Year, everyone.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 0 157 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}{f 4 23 0 6 0 25 25}I've never worn a kimono before...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
