    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 157 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}{f 4 23 0 7 0 25 25}What is this odd sensation I feel...?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_012_0_0" type="Message">
